{"id":"226611384_Unique_Sink_Orientations_of_Grids","abstract":"We introduce unique sink orientations of grids as digraph models for many well-studied problems, including linear programming\nover products of simplices, generalized linear complementarity problems over P-matrices (PGLCP), and simple stochastic games.\n\nWe investigate the combinatorial structure of such orientations and develop randomized algorithms for finding the sink. We\nshow that the orientations arising from PGLCP satisfy the Holt-Klee condition known to hold for polytope digraphs, and we\ngive the first expected linear-time algorithms for solving PGLCP with a fixed number of blocks.","authors":["Bernd Gärtner","Walter Morris","Leo Rüst"],"meta":["May 2005Algorithmica 51(2):200-235","DOI:10.1007/s00453-007-9090-x","SourceDBLP"],"references":["280445715_The_On-Line_Encyclopedia_of_Integer_Sequences","266429362_On_generalized_nonlinear_complementarity_problem","247889815_The_Generalized_Order_Linear_Complementarity_Problem","246722102_Long_Monotone_Paths_in_Abstract_Polytopes","242985794_Existence_theory_and_Q-matrix_characterization_for_the_generalized_linear_complementarity_problem_Revisited","239337077_A_proof_of_the_strict_monotone_4-step_conjecture","220915842_The_On-Line_Encyclopedia_of_Integer_Sequences","321610844_Automata_Logics_and_Infinite_Games_A_Guide_to_Current_Research","316518696_On_algorithms_for_simple_stochastic_games","269902039_The_Linear_Complementarity_Problem","268858476_Unimodal_set-functions","267972308_Automata_Logics_and_Infinite_Games","265716056_The_linear_complementarity_problem_An_introduction","262410128_Completely_unimodal_numberings_of_a_simple_polytope","260082669_Lectures_on_Polytopes","259365645_On_the_generalized_complementarity_problem","248896686_The_Linear_Complementarity_Problem_with_Interval_Data","246390061_How_good_is_the_simplex_algorithm_In_Inequalities","245952845_Distinguishing_cube_orientations_arising_from_linear_programs","244957865_A_Linear_Com